  "title": "Подготовить SDL_shadercross Native Distribution",
  "description": "## T-0947 [ ] P0: Подготовить SDL_shadercross Native Distribution\n\n- Создана: 2026-07-05T03:32:25+03:00\n- Состояние: open\n- Приоритет: P0\n- Execution class: `internal-substrate`\n- Scheduling tier: `final-gate`\n- Зависимости: T-0241, T-0243, T-0245, T-0246\n- Ссылки:\n  - Доменный документ: `docs/quality/godot-47-sdl-shadercross-native-distribution.md`\n  - Документация/API index: `data/documentation/`; `data/api/`\n  - Исходный код: `src/Electron2D/`; `eng/`\n  - Тесты и проверки производительности: `tests/`\n  - ROADMAP: раздел `2. Публичный API` / `2.21 Diagnostics, CI, Packaging And Compatibility Policy`\n\n### Execution contract\n\n- Task type: production\n- Ready-to-start:\n  - task state is `open` or an explicitly defined ready state.\n  - dependencies are accepted/closed or have explicit `Deferred`/`Unsupported` contract.\n  - docs/quality/godot-47-sdl-shadercross-native-distribution.md is current and RED tests/verifiers can be added before production changes.\n- Stop conditions:\n  - implementation requires a sibling task, unrelated subsystem, blocked platform prerequisite or public API surface outside generated packets.\n  - tests, domain document or generated source-of-truth artifacts are missing or stale.\n  - a shortcut would introduce facade, stub, hidden fallback or undocumented behavior.\n- May change:\n  - files named in this task's `Ссылки` block and their owning tests/docs.\n  - generated artifacts only through their owning generator/verifier.\n  - `TASKS.md` notes/current evidence and diary entries for this task.\n- Must not change:\n  - neighboring public classes, unrelated internal substrates, release gates or tracking parent scope.\n  - public API surface not present in generated Godot 4.7 packets.\n  - unrelated formatting, dependency graph or metadata churn.\n- Required outputs:\n  - docs/quality/godot-47-sdl-shadercross-native-distribution.md\n  - RED/GREEN test or verifier evidence for the selected slice.\n  - synchronized XML/docs/API/generated documentation evidence when public surface or docs change.\n  - task notes/current evidence and diary entry with exact command results.\n- Required commands:\n  - `git diff --check`\n  - `dotnet run --project eng/Electron2D.Build -- verify docs`\n  - `dotnet run --project eng/Electron2D.Build -- update docs --check`\n  - `dotnet run --project eng/Electron2D.Build -- verify licenses` when C# source changes.\n- External audit:\n  - required for final acceptance unless a parent gate explicitly owns audit evidence\n\n### Самодостаточное описание\n\nЦель - сформировать и проверить `SDL_shadercross Native Distribution` как отдельный packaging/distribution contract для Public API 0.1-preview scope.\n\nЗадача не реализует поведение public classes и не добавляет public API. Она владеет только package inventory, platform/RID mapping, native/tooling dependency sources, generated package artifacts, checksum/file-list validation, verifier command, stable failure diagnostics and release/audit evidence.\n\n### Как выполнять задачу без дополнительного контекста\n\n- Источник истины: доменный документ из блока `Ссылки`, platform/RID matrix, package inventory, native dependency source URLs, versions, hashes and license rows.\n- Граница public API: задача упаковывает уже реализованные artifacts и не добавляет public API или runtime behavior.\n- Исполняемый результат: deterministic package generation or verification, file-list/checksum validation, stable failure diagnostics and release/audit evidence.\n- Runtime checks: runtime benchmarks не применяются, если package smoke explicitly не требует runtime execution; это фиксируется в доменном документе.\n\n### Границы задачи\n\n- Цель: подготовить только package/distribution contract `SDL_shadercross Native Distribution`, без реализации behavior packaged components.\n- Входит: package inventory, platform/RID mapping, source URL/version/hash/license rows where applicable, deterministic artifact verification and stable diagnostics.\n- Не входит: runtime/backend implementation, public API additions, unrelated platform support and manual package repairs.\n- Подтверждение приёмки: package file list, checksums, verifier output, dependency inventory and release/audit evidence.\n\n### Первичные потребители результата\n\n- Release packaging, audit package verification and platform smoke gates consume package artifacts from `SDL_shadercross Native Distribution`.\n- Consumers must receive file-list/checksum validation, dependency inventory and stable failure diagnostics.\n- Доменный документ должен назвать artifact paths, verifier command and release/audit consumer evidence.\n\n### Internal substrate acceptance contract\n\n- `SDL_shadercross Native Distribution` has deterministic init/success and fail-closed diagnostics in the domain document, including a stable `E2D-*` code family when runtime failure is possible.\n- First consumer proof names the public task, required internal capability and first test/report that proves the consumer uses this substrate instead of a fallback.\n- Resource lifetime, cache, handle or subscription counters return to baseline after the smallest create/use/dispose scenario applicable to this substrate.\n- Unsupported platform/backend paths return documented diagnostics and do not silently degrade into stubs or no-op behavior.\n- This task does not define public methods/properties/signals/enums; public behavior remains owned by the concrete public API tasks.\n### Критерии приёмки\n\n- [ ] Доменный документ `docs/quality/godot-47-sdl-shadercross-native-distribution.md` фиксирует task-specific scope `SDL_shadercross Native Distribution`, source inventory, generated report/artifact, verifier command, consumers, unsupported/deferred rows and release/audit evidence.\n- [ ] Deterministic generation or verification command воспроизводимо создаёт report/artifact/log для `SDL_shadercross Native Distribution` и fails on stale, missing or manually edited outputs.\n- [ ] Package inventory содержит platform/RID mapping, native/tooling dependency source URL, version, hash, license row and expected artifact path where applicable.\n- [ ] Generated artifact validation проверяет schema/file list/checksum/source links as applicable and produces stable diagnostics without secret leakage.\n- [ ] Release/audit consumer evidence показывает, какой gate, package check or report consumes `SDL_shadercross Native Distribution` and how failures become actionable.\n- [ ] Runtime benchmarks не требуются, если `SDL_shadercross Native Distribution` не запускает runtime path; доменный документ содержит явную not-applicable строку вместо фиктивных замеров критических путей.\n- [ ] Документация, generated documentation index or task notes синхронизированы с фактическим контрактом `SDL_shadercross Native Distribution`.\n- [ ] Проверки текущей задачи фиксируются в дневнике: целевые verifier/test commands, нужные проверки сборки, документации и лицензий and `git diff --check`.\n\n### Подзадачи\n\n- [ ] Зафиксировать task-specific source inventory, consumers, generated artifact paths, verifier command and explicit out-of-scope в доменном документе.\n- [ ] Добавить или обновить verifier/test fixtures, которые сначала доказывают текущий разрыв, затем проходят на рабочем generator/check/artifact validation path.\n- [ ] Реализовать deterministic generator/check/report or explicit `Deferred`/`Unsupported` contract for `SDL_shadercross Native Distribution` without adding public API.\n- [ ] Проверить generated artifacts, no secret leakage, release/audit evidence and runtime-benchmark applicability decision.\n- [ ] Обновить документацию и выполнить релевантные проверки.\n\n### Заметки агента\n\n2026-07-05T03:32:25+03:00 - Создано по результатам проверки целевого списка: этот явно названный объём раньше не имел отдельной активной задачи в предыдущем срезе ROADMAP.\n\n",
